description: Gaston Corbala is the Founder & Owner of GreenGo Inc., the company responsible for the GreenGo Grilled Cheese Food Truck.The 1st Grilled Cheese Food Truck in San Diego.  Our goal is simple- take pride in what we make.  And what is that? – Serving a funky, unique and very delicious American Classic- the grilled cheese.EcoFriendly GreenGo is proud of taking care of you and the environment. We take pride in bringing you the finest quality in all of our products, using local and organic products whenever possible.
name: GreenGo Grilled Cheese
